thread.title: Treasury to Sell $186 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $186 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $186 billion in securities next week, comprising $108 billion in new debt and $78 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $48 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Nov. 9, 2017, maturing May 10, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PF0.
